<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>上宾自营销</title>
  <link rel="Shortcut Icon" href="public/images/i/favicon.ico"/>
  <!-- 新 Bootstrap 核心 CSS 文件 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/css/login.css"/>

</head>

<body class="center-block">
<div class="bg-green">
  <div class="margin">
      <div class="box-dark">
        <img src="./public/images/login/shangbinlogo.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <!--<img src="./public/img/exchange.png" alt="" class="transform">-->

      <div class="box-light">
        <div>
          <img src="./public/images/login/weixin.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="text"> 请先通过上宾账号登录</div>
        <div class="form-inline">
          <div class="form-group has-feedback">
            <div class="input-group">
              <span class="input-group-addon"><img src="public/images/login/user.png"></span>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="账号">
            </div>
            <br/>

            <div class="input-group">
              <span class="input-group-addon"><img src="public/images/login/lock.png"></span>
              <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="密码">
            </div>
            <br>

            <div class="error"></div>
            <div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg">登录</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <footer>
      <hr>
      <div class="green">为什么要授权绑定？</div>
      <div>绑定微信公众账号后，顾客便可在贵店主页中直接关注本店公众账号，便捷接受宣传信息与管理个人权益</div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- jQuery文件。务必在bootstrap.min.js 之前引入 -->
<script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
<!-- 最新的 Bootstrap 核心 JavaScript 文件 -->
<script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="public/js/md5.js"></script>
<script src="public/js/cookie.min.js"></script>
<script src="public/js/config.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
